c + o = u
n + o = t
L + i = n  // 14

Star Trek + The Dusty Defiant = Star Trek: The Dusty Defiant
Star Trek: The Dusty Defiant + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Star Trek: The Next Dusty Generation

5 - The Phoenix: 
Star Trek + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Star Trek: Deep Space Nine
Star Trek: Deep Space Nine + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Star Trek: Generations
Star Trek: Deep Space Nine + Star Trek: Generations = Star Trek: First Contact
Locomotive + Star Trek: First Contact = Zefram Cochrane
Star Trek: Generations + Zefram Cochrane = The Phoenix

5 - The First Warp Flight: 
Star Trek + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Star Trek: Deep Space Nine
Star Trek: Deep Space Nine + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Star Trek: Generations
Star Trek: Deep Space Nine + Star Trek: Generations = Star Trek: First Contact
Locomotive + Star Trek: First Contact = Zefram Cochrane
Star Trek: The Next Generation + Zefram Cochrane = The First Warp Flight

5 - Quorail, Trek: 
Earth + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Data
Data + Data = Information
Information + Q = Quora
Quora + Train = Quorail
Quorail + Star Trek = Quorail, Trek

5 - Quorail System: 
Earth + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Data
Data + Data = Information
Information + Q = Quora
Quora + Train = Quorail
Quorail + Solar System = Quorail System

5 - The Defiant Next Milky Way: 
Star Trek + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Star Trek: Deep Space Nine
Locomotive + Star Trek: Deep Space Nine = The Defiant
Solar System + The Defiant = The Milky Way
Star Trek: The Next Generation + The Milky Way = The Next Milky Way
The Defiant + The Next Milky Way = The Defiant Next Milky Way

5 - Qututus: 
Locomotive + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Locutus
Fire + Locutus = Borg
Borg + Q = Qborg
Locutus + Qborg = Qutus
Locutus + Qutus = Qututus

5 - Qutusborg: 
Locomotive + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Locutus
Fire + Locutus = Borg
Borg + Q = Qborg
Locutus + Qborg = Qutus
Qborg + Qutus = Qutusborg

5 - Loco Wind: The Next Generation: 
Locomotive + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Locutus
Locomotive + Locutus = Loco
Loco + Star Trek = Loco Trek
Loco Trek + Wind = Loco Wind
Loco Wind + Star Trek: The Next Generation = Loco Wind: The Next Generation
